data.description: Conveniently located lock and leave condo right in the center of Grand Junction! Walking distance to Colorado Mesa University, less than 10 min from GJT Airport, Downtown, and the Mesa Mall. Powderhorn Ski Resort, the Colorado National Monument, and Highline State Park all an hour or less away!  Enjoy hot summer days next to the recently upgraded pool and BBQ facility, or a short drive to Palisade for a winery tour. In the winter months maintenance is provided making this a hassle free property year round.   This would also make a great investment or second home for a CMU student. Come take a look!
